<tr><td>Foot</td><td>Plantarflexes, inverts, adducts</td></tr>
<tr><td>Ankle</td><td>Plantarflexes, inverts, adducts</td></tr>
<tr><td>Knee</td><td>Extends, abducts, externally rotates</td></tr>
