    <line x1="40" y1="36" x2="40" y2="70" stroke="#c9a227" stroke-width="3"/>
    <line x1="160" y1="36" x2="160" y2="70" stroke="#c9a227" stroke-width="3"/>
    <text x="100" y="118" text-anchor="middle" fill="#e6c659" font-size="11">holds &#8212; no length change</text>
  </g>
</svg>
<figcaption>The three muscle actions. In this guide's tables: <span class="pill p-conc">Concentric</span> = isolated function (accelerate), <span class="pill p-ecc">Eccentric</span> = integrated function (decelerate), <span class="pill p-iso">Isometric</span> = integrated function (stabilize).</figcaption>
